    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">This Buckshot Knives Lightweight Hatchet is prefect for your backpacking, camping, and hunting needs.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor Camping Axe Hatchet Multi Tool Black Steel With Cord Cutter</h2>\n  <p>This Buckshot Knives Lightweight Hatchet is prefect for your backpacking, camping, and hunting needs.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>STAINLESS STEEL BLADE - Stainless steel axe blade is durable and easy to maintain</li>\n    <li>OUTDOOR USE - Lightweight body makes this ideal for Camping, Hunting, and Hiking</li>\n    <li>VERSATILE - Includes 3 hex holes that function as an easy-to-use emergency wrench. Also features a cord cutter in the butt of the handle</li>\n    <li>AXE HEADCOVER - Nylon Sheath with a belt-loop axe headcover included</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS - Blade Length:</strong> 4-Inches, Overall Length: 10-Inches, Grip Length: 4-Inch</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/10347/H10326f9b4b5c4a14aa0a22eb697c6f1ao.jpg\" alt=\"This Buckshot Knives Lightweight Hatchet is prefect for your backpacking, camping, and hunting needs\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> H-8905676</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 615602984513</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Black</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>The 4&quot; blade and 10.5&quot; full tang steel body gives you plenty of chopping potential. The handle has a stylish two piece real wood grip for a comfortable feel, and includes a lanyard hole.</p>\n  <p>The head of the axe includes 3 hex holes, allowing this hatchet to be used as a wrench in an emergency, reducing the overall weight for those long days of hiking. The butt of the axe also includes a cord cutter / gut hook for added versatility.</p>\n  <p>Additional features include a nylon sheath with a belt loop and a ridged thumb rest above the wooden grip for added dexterity.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
